      <p class="proj-eyebrow">More Projects</p>
      <h2 class="proj-h2">Three more sites.<br/><span class="proj-h2-dim">Built, live, and loved.</span></h2>
      <p class="proj-sub">Each one started with a free 24-hour sample. Each one launched within a week.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Project cards -->
    <div class="proj-grid">

      <!-- ── CARD 1: CHICKEN CONNECTION ── -->
      <div class="proj-card proj-reveal" style="--card-delay:0.05s">
        <div class="proj-card-screens">
          <!-- Main screen -->
          <div class="proj-main-screen">
            <div class="proj-chrome">
              <div class="proj-chrome-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
              <div class="proj-chrome-url">Sample Preview</div>
            </div>
            <div class="proj-img-wrap">
              <img src="/work/chicken.png" alt="Chicken Connection website" class="proj-main-img" loading="lazy"/>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Peek strips: 2 more screenshots stacked at bottom -->
          <div class="proj-peek-row">
            <div class="proj-peek">
              <img src="/work/chicken2.png" alt="Chicken Connection — menu section" loading="lazy"/>
            </div>
            <div class="proj-peek">
              <img src="/work/chicken3.png" alt="Chicken Connection — story page" loading="lazy"/>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Hover overlay -->
          <div class="proj-card-hover-overlay">
            <span class="proj-view-btn">View project →</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="proj-card-meta">
          <div class="proj-card-tags">
            <span class="proj-tag proj-tag-orange">Restaurant</span>
            <span class="proj-tag proj-tag-ghost">Sample</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="proj-card-title">Chicken Connection</h3>
          <p class="proj-card-body">40-year Marshall institution. Built their first real website with online ordering, a story page, and the bold identity they deserved.</p>
          <div class="proj-card-specs">
            <div class="proj-spec"><span class="proj-spec-n">5</span><span class="proj-spec-l">Days live</span></div>
            <div class="proj-spec-sep"></div>
            <div class="proj-spec"><span class="proj-spec-n">3</span><span class="proj-spec-l">Pages built</span></div>
            <div class="proj-spec-sep"></div>
            <div class="proj-spec"><span class="proj-spec-n">$0</span><span class="proj-spec-l">Up front</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ── CARD 2: PHOTOWORKS ── -->
